#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "This module is used to enable and configure desktop effects for Plasma."
msgstr ""
"See moodul võimaldab sisse lülitada ja seadistada Plasma töölauaefekte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The main part of this page is a list of all available effects grouped by "
#| "<guilabel>Accessibility</guilabel>, <guilabel>Appearance</guilabel>, "
#| "<guilabel>Focus</guilabel>, <guilabel>Tools</guilabel>, <guilabel>Candy</"
#| "guilabel> and <guilabel>Window Management</guilabel>."
msgid ""
"The main part of this page is a list of all available effects grouped by "
"<guilabel>Accessibility</guilabel>, <guilabel>Appearance</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Focus</guilabel>, <guilabel>Peek at Desktop Animation</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Tools</guilabel>, <guilabel>Virtual Desktop Switching Animation</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Window Management</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Window Open/"
"Close Animation</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Selle kaardi põhiosa toob ära kõik saadaolevad efektid, mis on rühmitatud "
"pealkirjade <guilabel>Hõlbustus</guilabel>, <guilabel>Välimus</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Fookus</guilabel>, <guilabel>Tööriistad</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Silmailu</guilabel> ja <guilabel>Aknahaldus</guilabel> alla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the incremental search bar above the list window to find items in the "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Akna ülaosas oleva otsingukastiga saab kiiresti leida loendist vajaliku "
"elemendi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Normally there is no reason for users to change that, but there is a "
#| "<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-filter.png"
#| "\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> configuration "
#| "button to modify the filtering of the list to show also those effects."
msgid ""
"Normally there is no reason for users to change that, but there is a "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-effects.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> configuration button to "
"modify the filtering of the list to show also those effects."
msgstr ""
"Tavaliselt pole kasutajal põhjust seda muuta, kuid on olemas seadistamisnupp "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-filter.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ka nimekirja "
"filtreerimise muutumiseks, et kõik efektid näha oleksid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The easiest way of installing new effects is by using the built-in "
#| "KNewStuff support in &kwin;. Press the <guibutton>Get New Effects</"
#| "guibutton> button to open a dialog with a list of available effects from "
#| "the Internet and to install and uninstall effects."
msgid ""
"The easiest way of installing new effects is by using the built-in KNewStuff "
"support in &kwin;. Press the <guibutton>Get New Desktop Effects</guibutton> "
"button to open a dialog with a list of available effects from the Internet "
"and to install and uninstall effects."
msgstr ""
"Lihtsaim viis uusi efekte paigaldada on kasutada &kwin;i sisseehitatud uue "
"kuuma kraami hankimise toetust. Klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Hangi uusi efekte</"
"guibutton>, mis avab dialoogi, kus näeb internetis saadaolevate efektide "
"loendit ning saab neid paigaldada ja eemaldada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please keep in mind that changing these sensible defaults can break your "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Palun arvesta, et nende mõistlike vaikeväärtuste muutmine võib sinu süsteemi "
"täiesti katki teha."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check an effect in the list to enable it. Display information about Author "
"and License by clicking the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"dialog-information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> info button at the right side of the list item."
msgstr ""
"Efekti sisselülitamiseks märgi see loendis. Autori ja litsentsi kohta saab "
"teavet, kui klõpsata loendikirjest paremal asuvale teabenupule "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"dialog-information.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some effects have settings options, in this case there is a "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"configure-effects.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> configure button at "
"the left of the info button. Click it to open a configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Mõne efekti juures on võimalik ka üht-teist seadistada, millisel juhul on "
"teabenupust vasakul seadistamisnupp <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"configure-effects.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>. Sellele klõpsates avaneb seadistustedialoog."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see a video preview of an effect click on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"video.png\" format=\"PNG"
"\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button."
msgstr ""
"Efekti videoeelvaatluse nägemiseks tuleb klõpsata nupule "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"video.png\" format=\"PNG"
"\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Some effects are mutual exclusive to other effects. For example one would "
#| "only want to activate the <guilabel>Minimize Animations</guilabel> or the "
#| "<guilabel>Magic Lamp</guilabel> effect. Both activated at the same time "
#| "result in broken animations."
msgid ""
"Some effects are mutual exclusive to other effects. For example one would "
"only want to activate the <guilabel>Maximize</guilabel> or the "
"<guilabel>Magic Lamp</guilabel> effect. Both activated at the same time "
"result in broken animations."
msgstr ""
"Mõned efektid on omavahel välistavad. Näiteks saab korraga aktiveerida "
"ainult kas <guilabel>animatsioonide minimeerimise</guilabel> või "
"<guilabel>võlulambi</guilabel> efekti. Katse mõlemat korraga aktiveerida "
"lõpeks katkise animatsiooniga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For effects in a mutual exclusive group the &GUI; uses radio buttons and "
"manages that only one of these effects can be activated."
msgstr ""
"Vastastikku välistavate efektide korral kasutatakse raadionuppe, millega "
"tagatakse, et korraga saab sisse lülitada neist ainult ühe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "All effects which are not supported by the currently used compositing "
#| "backend are hidden by default (&eg; OpenGL effects when using XRender)."
msgid ""
"All effects which are not supported by the currently used compositing "
"backend are hidden by default (&eg; OpenGL effects when using software "
"renderer)."
msgstr ""
"Kõik efektid, mida parajasti kasutatav komposiidi taustaprogramm ei toeta, "
"on vaikimisi peidetud (&eg; OpenGL-i efektid, kui kasutusel on XRender)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also all internal or helper effects are hidden by default. These are effects "
"which replace functionality from KWin Core or provide interaction with other "
"elements of the desktop shell."
msgstr ""
"Samuti on vaikimisi peidetud kõik sisemised või abiefektid. Need on efektid, "
"mis asendavad KWin Core funktsionaalsust või võimaldavad interaktiivset "
"suhtlemist töölauakesta teiste elementidega."
